who sold his first
internet companies

00:01:49,910 --> 00:01:53,530
for over $350 million.

00:01:53,530 --> 00:01:55,410
And Mark Cuban,

00:01:55,410 --> 00:01:57,830
notorious billionaire
entrepreneur

00:01:57,830 --> 00:02:13,580
