of the Dallas Mavericks.

00:02:13,580 --> 00:02:16,330
First into the Shark Tank
is Aaron Krause,

00:02:16,330 --> 00:02:19,697
who believes his product will
make every day cleaning easier.

00:02:24,110 --> 00:02:27,250
