a $100,000 investment

00:02:35,860 --> 00:02:39,110
in exchange for 10% equity
in the Scrub Daddy business.

00:02:39,110 --> 00:02:40,830
It's the greatest
kitchen scrubbing tool

00:02:40,830 --> 00:02:42,160
