00:03:23,910 --> 00:03:26,200
And it's gonna cut
right through that.

00:03:27,410 --> 00:03:28,680
It won't scratch
any of your surfaces

00:03:28,680 --> 00:03:30,683
but it will clean them
beautifully.

00:03:30,683 --> 00:03:33,700
Now Scrub Daddy's
not really smiling anymore,

00:03:33,700 --> 00:03:34,680
