forks, spatulas,

00:03:56,700 --> 00:03:59,450
even large serving spoons
on both sides

00:03:59,450 --> 00:04:00,780
at the same time.

00:04:00,780 --> 00:04:02,947
Sharks, with your help,

00:04:02,947 --> 00:04:04,727
Scrub Daddy will
be scrubbing and smiling

00:04:04,727 --> 00:04:06,617
in every kitchen
in the world.

00:04:06,617 --> 00:04:08,777
Whoo!
(Daymond and Lori) Wow!

00:04:08,777 --> 00:04:11,314
Scrub Daddy!
I've never witnessed
a live infomercial.

00:04:11,314 --> 00:04:13,527
That was fantastic.

00:04:13,527 --> 00:04:16,100
That was incredible.
Do you have samples?

00:04:16,100 --> 00:04:19,068
