00:05:17,433 --> 00:05:19,296
I know exactly what
I need to do

00:05:19,296 --> 00:05:20,596
to make this thing
really efficient,

00:05:20,596 --> 00:05:21,043
and I'm looking to add
a strategic partner

00:05:21,043 --> 00:05:24,626
who can open this up
into the retail stores.

00:05:24,626 --> 00:05:27,096
I'm only in five supermarkets.
That's it.

00:05:27,096 --> 00:05:28,756
