like dobie pads

00:05:58,145 --> 00:06:01,203
or other pads out there
that are, you know, brand-name.

00:06:01,203 --> 00:06:03,953
Scrub Daddy, I-I think
you've done a great job today,

00:06:03,953 --> 00:06:05,903
but I don't know if it's
gonna work in retail.

00:06:05,903 --> 00:06:07,363
I don't--I don't buy in
for that vision.

00:06:09,113 --> 00:06:10,953
Just in the packaging,

00:06:10,953 --> 00:06:12,983
I just don't know if I see
the difference.
Robert, I--

00:06:12,983 --> 00:06:15,203
it doesn't sell on a shelf--
Correct.

00:06:15,203 --> 00:06:17,113
But if you put it
in display shippers

00:06:17,113 --> 00:06:18,283
which we've built--

00:06:18,283 --> 00:06:19,903
These beautiful
cardboard display shippers--

00:06:19,903 --> 00:06:21,613
and it communicates the message
to every one of the customers.

00:06:21,613 --> 00:06:23,313
It sits on the end cabin.

00:06:23,313 --> 00:06:24,150
You're gonna have to pay
for those things.

00:06:24,150 --> 00:06:26,145
Well...
it's hard to get them,

00:06:26,145 --> 00:06:28,653
even if you pay for them.

00:06:28,653 --> 00:06:31,363
Great job today, but I-I don't
see the retail vision.

00:06:31,363 --> 00:06:32,813
I'm out.

00:06:34,141 --> 00:06:37,063
I understand.

00:06:37,063 --> 00:06:38,733
I like the product.

00:06:38,733 --> 00:06:40,113
I think you're--You're doing
great things.

00:06:40,113 --> 00:06:41,145
