completely dependent on QVC,

00:06:48,153 --> 00:06:50,136
that's a disaster
waiting to happen.

00:06:50,136 --> 00:06:54,453
Well, I-I've got 3,000 stores
lined up right now.

00:06:54,453 --> 00:06:57,363
We're gonna be
in 3,000 stores.

00:06:57,363 --> 00:06:58,783
I understand, but even...

00:06:58,783 --> 00:06:59,136
